## Trainings (Requer Autenticação)

### Listar Todos
```http
GET /api/trainings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
```

### Buscar por ID
```http
GET /api/trainings/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
```

### Meus Trainings
```http
GET /api/trainings/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
```

### Criar Training (Admin)
```http
POST /api/trainings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Python para Data Science",
  "description": "Curso completo de Python focado em análise de dados"
}
```

### Atualizar Training (Admin)
```http
PUT /api/trainings/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Desenvolvimento Web Full Stack 2026",
  "description": "Curso atualizado com tecnologias modernas"
}
```

### Deletar Training (Admin)
```http
DELETE /api/trainings/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
```

