## Exemplos cURL

### Login e obter token
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/student/login \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{"email":"joao.silva@email.com","password":"password123"}'
```

### Listar trainings com token
```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/api/trainings \
  -H 'Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE'
```

### Criar enrollment
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/enrollments \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -H 'Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE' \
  -d '{"classId":1,"studentId":1}'
```
